Name: Numberline 3
About the game: Numberline 3 is hard, but very interesting puzzle game, which will force your mind work for all 100%. You have to repeat a mosaic, but it is not very easy. You relax and listen good soundtrack in the beginning and levels are seems to be easy, but after a few levels the game becomes difficult and more exciting! This part of series challange you to deal with hexagons. It gives us a possibility to create much difference in levels for you. Also, clear tutorial await you. Game features: - Unique gameplay - Neon design - A large number of levels - Calm music - Simple tutorial
